===Using Pybugs to control Gentoo bugreports===

The [https://github.com/williamh/pybugz README] in the repository of {{Package|www-client/pybugz}} gives a good introduction into the configuration and commands.

==== attach a file to a bug====
{{cmd
|bugz attach -c "text/plain" -d "build log" $bugnumber $log
}}
